caption: We came all the way from Raleigh NC to try out Jimmy Pearls, and man was it worth it!!!!! We were going to come in for the 4:00 I believe dinner menu and by the time we got there at 4:16ish, they were sold out!!!! Dude they were sold out …

After seeing their fish sandwich all over Instagram, we had to come in and check it out before they left 7th street market.  Covid-19: you can order and pay online. They do curbside pickup too.  We got the Uncle Gene's Fish Sandwhich …
